snippet.title: NegativeNedTV
snippet.description: Negative Ned is the living characterization of the ideals of negativity and cynicism which continue to grow in our current world today. He is everything we should strive not to be, but through no fault of our own continues to exist in all of us in one moment or another. This channel stands to represent the darker and pessimistic side of people, and what indulging too much into this side can eventually turn you into. In other words, just don't be a dickhead like Ned and try and see the bright side every once in a while ya emorific douche canoes!
